title: HABSHD Study Package
text: HABSHD R package containing data code reproduce results Health & Aging Brain Study: Health Disparities (HABS-HD) study (O’Bryant et al. 2021). HABSHD bundle data, analysis code examples, html pdf documentation. html documentation viewable https://github.com/mcdonohue/HABSHD. data, including HABSHD R package, avalialable https://apps.unthsc.edu/itr/research/ registering agreeing data use agreement.

title: HABSHD Study Package
text: install HABSHD: Register https://apps.unthsc.edu/itr/research Download HABSHD_0.1.5.tar.gz https://apps.unthsc.edu/itr/research/ R, run install.packages("path//HABSHD_0.1.5.tar.gz", repos = NULL, type = "source") script build R package can found tools.
